= [[span class="bt"]]__ADDENDUM__:[[/span]] Debriefing Material

= Resubmit clearance credentials to access post-mission reports regarding SCP-6500-α acquisition.

[[div class="notation table1"]]
= **Status Update on [[span class="bt"]]Mouleur Foci[[/span]]**

= __Beats / Minute:__ 0.24

While SCP-6500-α-Heart is resistant to the majority of time dilation effects, ongoing research is proving fruitful in further lowering the Heart's beats per minute via temporal methods. Destruction or complete cessation of SCP-6500-α-Heart has been definitively forbidden by order of the O5 Council, due to the unknown potential effects on natural entropic phenomena.

Project Cardiac Arrest's efficacy since last reported values is as follows:

= __External Trends__

||~ Effect ||~ Rate ||~ Change ||
|| Affected anomaly neutralized by SCP-6500 || 0.86 / day || ##4b2|-342%## ||
|| New anomaly affected by SCP-6500 || 1.34 / day || ##4b2|-120%## ||
|| Way closed by SCP-6500 || 0.04 / day || ##4b2|-89%## ||
|| Failure or deviation of thaumaturgic practice || 18.06% || ##4b2|-50%## ||
|| Anomalous ideas forgotten || 4.80 terabytes / day || ##4b2|-48%## ||
|| Anomalous information corrupted || 80.62 petabytes / day || ##4b2|-30%## ||

= __Project Trends__

||~ Effect ||~ Rate ||~ Change ||
|| Personnel turnover rate || 7.0 / month || ##4b2|-11%## ||
|| Equipment failure rate || 19.2 / month || ##f24|+4%## ||
|| Reports of nausea || 83.0 / month || ##f24|+46%## ||
|| Reports of serious illness || 4.1 / month || ##4b2|-8%## ||
|| Hallucinations || 40.2 / month || ##f24|+24%## ||
|| Dreams || 28.9 / month || ##f24|+60%## ||
|| Production of corrosive fluids || 320 kg / day || ##f24|+176%## ||
|| Personnel casualty rate || 3.2 / month || ##4b2|-76%## ||
|| Attempts at parasitic attachment ||  4.8 / month || ##f24|+6%## ||
|| Attempts at escape ||  16.0 / month || ##f24|+34%## ||

= __Outliers & Notable Events:__

* SCP-6500-α-Heart breached containment with the aid of Junior Researcher ██████ who used a stolen security card to open the containment chamber. Shortly thereafter, SCP-6500-α-Heart was returned to containment without event, and Junior Researcher ██████ was brought in for interrogation. It was soon discovered that they were functionally dead despite their animation and bore no memories of the original Junior Researcher ██████. They have since been neutralized.

* SCP-6500-α-Heart accelerated its heart rate by 200% for two hours before emergency thaumaturgic measures were taken against it. It was soon discovered that SCP-6500-α-Heart had produced adrenaline instead of blood for this period of time, and the effect has been kept from repeating by a localized concept erasure of adrenaline from its containment cell.

* A corpse matching that of Dr. Arceo was discovered in SCP-6500-α-Heart's containment chamber after the simultaneous failure of all audiovisual devices. Dr. Arceo was contacted shortly after to confirm his status and whereabouts. The source of the matching corpse is unknown.

* Dr. Arceo now reports dreams of SCP-6500-α-Heart once every three days, though this rate is such an outlier that it has not been included among the rest of the data.

* A snorkel, covered in a thin layer of SCP-6500-α-Heart's corrosive fluids, was found in Dr. Arceo's office desk drawer.

