[[div class="jotting"]]
This project has been a massive success. SCP-6500's effects are being mitigated across the board with less than half the expected cost of what was previously thought possible. I can not thank my team enough, but I am sure there will be more opportunities for gratitude because the road ahead of us is long and as of yet uncertain. I am, however, confident we will pull through.

We have singlehandedly postponed the death of magic by at least several years, and we are looking forward to postponing it further. Nothing more I can say that I haven't said before. Godspeed, everyone.

[[>]]
//-- Dr. Logan Arceo//
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

